{"tid":764251,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得細個玩個一種遊戲","createTime":"2018-08-01T20:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T09:23:49.000Z","uid":56322,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6b764059b506c17464a48852f3f24b42aacb47fa","tid":764251,"uid":56322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:11:19.000Z","msg":"係幾個人，手牽手定掂您隔離兩個隻手<br />\n然後大家有規律一下一下拍手，每一下叫氣<br />\n儲夠氣可以出招打人消耗氣<br />\n例如向前面條友出斬，佢又可以用氣出擋<br />\n完全考反應<br />\n多氣d招勁d 要高氣d嘅擋<br />\n又咩元氣玉之類嘅野<br />\n叫乜乜魂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有好多呢d遊戲，咩see see sorry 並bom猜 又係唔記得 求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bbc640f1437ea13e9efe6d28a44bcac489de87","tid":764251,"uid":56322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:13:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1b3d9300118adf313668b32004450692a37fb59","tid":764251,"uid":56322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becc4e3b69ed1dce22e5cc8f12cb10183b9f90de","tid":764251,"uid":51989,"like":7,"dislike":33,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:17:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bec5df983493533de0b9c93ac5987ab6ff76f52","tid":764251,"uid":56322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:20:44.000Z","msg":"唔通我生活係平衡時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c72cfe981c9d9cd25243339c81996c1c39d0e9b","tid":764251,"uid":14797,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:31:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">007</span></strong>"},{"pid":"323229bc5bfc06208cc04edd3645b24a1e4ed3f0","tid":764251,"uid":13545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:33:14.000Z","msg":"玩過<br />\n<br />\n拍一下手 <br />\n然後可以 儲氣 或 擋<br />\n<br />\n最高好似可以儲4下<br />\n儲1下 出拳<br />\n儲2下 出腳<br />\n儲3下 出必殺<br />\n儲4下 出超必<br />\n頭3個可以擋 超必無得擋<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7188edeb5407ca34b2082872fd351bfe7eee53","tid":764251,"uid":100760,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:34:39.000Z","msg":"個你老母"},{"pid":"a3821f050253c5f9cba78d9c7dd430956e8a080e","tid":764251,"uid":53170,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:35:49.000Z","msg":"以前玩過 叫凌草<br />\n有儲氣<br />\n有忍<br />\n有擋<br />\n儲夠氣又有七旋斬同七旋擋"},{"pid":"9a4caaa8c33a5155c65af349cdeb0dcfeac241e7","tid":764251,"uid":119027,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:47:26.000Z","msg":"成個小息十幾個同學一齊玩<br />\n都唔知點解記得邊個入左幾多氣<br />\n玩到咁上下通常都係口同鼻嗌<br />\n嗰時係玩倚天屠龍記版本<br />\n又乾坤大挪移 倚天劍 屠龍刀<br />\n諗番起都好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb73c31621bfb1ebd4b6f4a698c99b787e9fc7c","tid":764251,"uid":10786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:50:45.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;必篤？&rdquo;"},{"pid":"6b1b76956ce410092c34b7b050a8141e4b5fc466","tid":764251,"uid":20805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T21:39:49.000Z","msg":"最9招式草一下氣直接打人<br />\n通常啲人第二行都係草氣"},{"pid":"69fb26d730ea3e66dc93d3e9d3109394637e84b3","tid":764251,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T21:49:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad176a2e62260b9a688a7b63cce6814744769fd0","tid":764251,"uid":4679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T22:05:28.000Z","msg":"零零七 入子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115008af7ea5cbf7ef0df0b51f4de9b8094bd6ec","tid":764251,"uid":36015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"323229